    C->>C: Transition to hover state
    U->>C: Click play button
    C->>C: Transition to active state
    C->>G: Trigger onPlay event
    G->>S: Start game session
    S-->>G: Game started
    G-->>C: Update to playing state
    C->>C: Show playing animation
```

